00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:43.000
One thing that often makes,

00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:44.000
if we're trying to explain

00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:45.000
something complicated,

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:46.000
